1971;;Die Screaming, Marianne;;American;;Pete Walker;;Susan George, Leo Genn;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Die_Screaming,_Marianne;;Marianne, a nightclub dancer, is on the run from vicious criminals. On her 21st birthday, she will inherit a vast fortune as well as some legal papers that will incriminate her father, a crooked judge. When her father invites Marianne to his estate in Portugal, a game of cat-and-mouse begins.[5]